        <updateDate>2010-04-13T21:13:33Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Volunteer Responder Incentive Protection Reauthorization Act of 2010 - Amends Internal Revenue Code provisions allowing a tax exclusion for benefits paid to volunteer firefighters and emergency medical providers by states and local government by: (1) increasing the amount of benefits excludible; and (2) extending such tax exclusion through 2013.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
